Class AbstractNumericalVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.AbstractVariable
      • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.AbstractNumericalVariable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Variable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DiscreteNumericalVariable, NumericalVariable

    @MappedSuperclass
public abstract class AbstractNumericalVariable
extends AbstractVariable
    Implements base properties (valid range and units) for Variable that has a numerical value.
